      "content": "i get that, but i already asked my doc and they were kind of vague about it. i'm just looking for supplements that are natural so they won't have crazy side effects like meds do. since St. John's Wort is just a plant, it shouldn't really clash with the sertraline, right? it's just most people's way of helping with mild cases.",
